              <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm" style="background-color: var(--surface); color: var(--text);">üá¨üáß English</span>
              <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm" style="background-color: var(--surface); color: var(--text);">üá´üá∑ French</span>
