              <div class="p-6 pb-3">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--text);">Product & Strategy</h3>
                <p class="mb-3" style="color: var(--muted);">From problem framing to GTM, turning ideas into products that matter.</p>
